g.text: Shows the list of tasks and freelancers, asking for the selection of a task
and a freelancer and asks for details of the execution of a task (e.g. end date,
delay, briefDescriptionQuality) and id of payment transaction .
select a task and a freelancer and introduce all data.
pt = newPaymentTransaction(task, freelancer, transId, endDate, delay, briefDescriptionQuality)
create(task, freelancer, transId, endDate, delay, briefDescriptionQuality)
shows the amount to be paid to the freelancer and asks for confirmation.
creates the payment transaction and informs the Collaborator of the success of the operation.
